Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯利克教主辅佐官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们特殊警察「狩人」奉大臣的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(425.06,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前来执行保护你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到被称为帝国最强的艾斯德斯将军会亲自前来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更安心的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经接收到「夜袭」潜入的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(440.96,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们狩杀他们之前 就借你几个房间来居住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必我府上一定不会让各位觉得无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对他们完全没有兴趣 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是想见见从刚刚开始 一直窥视我们的那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是被您发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几个人正是帝国派来帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让我掌握教团暴力的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇拳寺罗刹四鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想他们怎么没在帝都 原来是来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了将军前来护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下原本这些专任护卫的恶鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也能把他们用在进攻上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和「夜袭」战斗没有帝具的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(337.08,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们试过凭借自己的实力打倒过帝具使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管帝具的能力有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其使用者终究只是肉体凡胎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也就是说 肯定有很多战胜他们的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗刹四鬼是大臣私人雇佣的处罚人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如他们所说 他们的本领是铁板钉钉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们只要在府邸里悠闲地喝酒就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也是 无论有多辉煌的实绩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 不愧是艾斯德斯将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都快要迷上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都将这几个重要的棋子部署在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却还让我也来到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大臣那家伙 似乎非常重视这个宗教团体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我能再早点赶过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波鲁斯先生也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明明还有妻子和女儿在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟要怎么报告才好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是威尔之所以会被打飞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是为了保护黑瞳小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长也决定这次的事件既往不咎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你的心情 但你先冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说她能坚持到现在 应该没有生命的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我试着解剖回收来的刺客的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还不能查明其来历
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是帝具使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该「夜袭」其中一员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(382.66,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 总之那恶人的尸体拿来喂小可可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑…黑瞳！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息了一下 好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本恢复过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的要害可是被扎中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我陪你继续同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所见 我还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:05:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你要跟过来 你就得好好努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十分钟之后 出发前往杰洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然还是在勉强自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是不要参与战线的战斗比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去跟队长说一说 让她给你脱离任务…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀部队的人 一旦被判定无法战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会连同以封口为由 处理掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什！？处理？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果脱离「狩人」的话 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(405.98,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有告诉队长 她一定会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样是不行的 我必须要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不要被处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是为了那样死去 才诞生于世的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算死 也是要在战斗中死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我的同伴们那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔 我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要伤口愈合的话 就能完全恢复如初的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说在这种离帝都那么远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会张贴大家的通缉令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定「狩人」会在这里新派发呢 切记掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(255.763,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才刚说完 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是神经绷得那么紧 也会很危险的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们表现出那样的气氛 对方也是能察觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是再自然一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明切尔茜死了 他明明是那么悲伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经平复下来 全心投入新的任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成长了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这也有一些道理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 这是帝都里没有的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这里的人比帝都的人更有活力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏有地下资源和宗教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗教？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎很赚钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然最终大部分的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因为欧尼斯特大臣从中操作 都纳入他囊里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 他们不知道自己被人利用着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道真相的反对派 都被伯利克镇压住无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就需要我们作为突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先好好了解这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 接下来就去外围逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好 圣堂附近的危险地带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给自告奋勇的拉伯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这城市就像迷宫一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过人这么多 方便混入探索 真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好我的名字面貌都没暴露过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底搜索 提高我在娜杰塔心里的分数
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉伯 你做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 朱天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的行动像不像在查探周围的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的直觉说他就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的脚步才是最可疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是经历过众多修罗场的人的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他似乎有所注意 但我能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他就是敌人呢 去把他杀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说错了 马头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是「解放他的灵魂」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据调查 在这个墓地的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有地下通道接通圣堂和伯利克的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要知道通道的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来就能去到伯利克的宅邸的地下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很难找到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这里这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下通道亦有可能部署了陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我没发现你吗 赤瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棘 你来杰洛克了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让我高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都在暗杀部队的时候几乎没说过话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是在最后的决战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀大臣时才会和你们罗刹四鬼对阵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛了帝国的坏孩子要打屁屁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬送！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们罗刹四鬼不仅进行了惨烈的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还喝着栖息于寺院后山的水怪克拉做的汤成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们能自由操纵身体！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 居然突然袭击我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子 你就只会四处逃窜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 已经死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太没劲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 快点离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那拳我用身上的线织铠甲挡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脉搏也用「交叉之尾」进入身体绑住血管 让其停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果只是不必在意的杂鱼啊 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走 你还要我装死装到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 朱天 另一个人去你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也是叛乱分子的密探
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是原本要和我汇合的女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我没法救你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然身为密探 你也应该做好这种觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是现世的迷途羔羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来解放你的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你尽情高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能对女性同伴见死不救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脉搏应该已经停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太笨了 明明你一直装死就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 考虑到自己的职务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直极力回避正面战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要是遇到必须要战斗的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是会战到底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个一起放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那把刀真不祥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「村雨」倒是和你般配嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 来吧 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 赤瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了我进行过惨烈的修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 没收帝具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这刀是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成你的目标就是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才故意放开帝具的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你刚才说「村雨」是不祥的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就觉得你们相性不合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不受这把被诅咒的刀的喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定你应该庆幸自己的罪孽还不重 棘…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个危险的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快要喜欢上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷袭行不通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「狩人」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424.757,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认「夜袭」的赤瞳潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(381.6,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的职责是侦察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经清楚地见识到你的「村雨」了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗刹四鬼加上「狩人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(502.743,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家都没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么放马过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不已经展开丝线开始攻击了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来解放你的灵魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇拳寺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百裂拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 我可没叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真灵巧的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那丝线是帝具吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说你是「夜袭」的一员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(457.314,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这次就打碎你的头颅 彻底杀掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种受欢迎的形式 真想求放过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的丝线啊 捆集起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起舞吧 离心力！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这招式太大破绽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不见得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超奥义「丝线冲击」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点程度就叫是绝招 别让人发笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗 我的目的已经达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你们的后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我也在此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让那个女人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才特意用那夸张的演技来吸引我们的注意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只有你一个 也要解放你的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗 这么气势汹汹地追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的丝线据称是用栖息在东海云层上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超危险种的体毛制造而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别保护要害的体毛 是极为坚韧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这部分体毛做成的丝线 实在是过于锋利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以被称为「界断丝」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我珍藏的一根 即使是你也切不断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太嫩了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这经过重重修行的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会被这些伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和身体有多强壮没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要被「交叉之尾」刺中胸部的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丝线就会朝你的心脏割去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来心脏部分没经过锻炼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能打倒朱天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下我要被大臣责骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你不用担这个心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然帝具被你看到了 就不能让你活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没什么抱歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是杀手的话这是很正常的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这液体怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为液体的重量导致丝线变松垮 发挥不了作用！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说这是油 应该说是我的汗液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗刹四鬼很擅长这样的身体操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话防御结界就起不了作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站…站不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再受到攻击的话 我必死无疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别垂死挣扎 太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是敌人的话 早就搭讪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不讨厌你这种类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会答应你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就等来世再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在匕首上绑了丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说回收丝线的话 匕首也一起跟着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点离开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可惜了 为什么我总是遇到这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然巡看很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但像近道和暗道 还有很多要查的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才需要调查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是购物的话 走多久都没问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你购物的时间太长 陪你一起逛太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？那是一般啦 一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法容忍女性购物的男人 胸襟太狭窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻嘲弄男人胸襟狭窄的女人才是胸襟狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意！我让你好好分清上下关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跟同伴分上下关系 就已经错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我注意一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请停止无谓的争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道我是多管闲事 但还是忍不住说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是「安宁道」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教主大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有时会像这样巡视街道周边的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看得出来 你们是被红线牵连着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以比起吵架 你们应该先互相告白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为情侣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得偶尔争吵一次也未尝不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要和这种家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是 才不要和你成为情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得你们很匹配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被选为担任教主大人的随从这光荣的职位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能近距离看到教主大人所引发的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你还有不净的邪念附身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就配不起这个职位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的衣服全脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用神圣的仪式帮你净身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 伯利克大人 有劳您了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过一点时间 就能完全掌控教团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我最大限度享受一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯利克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在进行神圣的仪式途中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于罗刹四鬼的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅一个晚上就有三个被对方杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还是小看「夜袭」了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(502.743,437)\fs21}Night Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然能给那群为非作歹的恶党施予正义铁槌的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们「狩人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(486.843,437)\fs21}Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜杰塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然途中中了你的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里我要把你的伙伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部蹂躏掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(435,310)\fsp15\an8\fad(300,0)\bord1\1c&H1C1379&\3c&HFFFFFF&\clip(0,300,848,326)}斩断因缘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(435,310)\fsp15\an8\fad(300,0)\bord1\1c&H0F0F0F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\clip(0,326,848,370)}斩断因缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:57.60,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}朽ち果てるように燃ゆる月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:04.41,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}暁に沈みゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:10.84,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\fs20\pos(358,444)}かお
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:10.84,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}造られた仮面で そっと近付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:16.16,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}信じるモノを 闇に落とす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:21.43,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}糸に絡まる エモノのように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:26.84,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}ただ ひたすらに 空を仰ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:34.86,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}繰り返される悲劇 不気味に笑う裏の顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:44.58,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}これ以上 何ひとつ 失くさないように刀を抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:50.19,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}闇に葬れ 汚れた笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:55.63,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}やり場のない怒り、放て！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:02:00.97,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}どれだけの 血と涙を流したら…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:05.98,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}祈るように 斬り裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:12.53,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}今日もアカク染め上げよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.42,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}振り返る過去はない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:15.04,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}この手 放した日から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.94,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}失うものはないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:25.18,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}繰り返し言い聞かせてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:31.82,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}静寂に漂う月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:37.18,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}どんな闇も 照らしてゆける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:42.36,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}強い光 未来へかざす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:47.18,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}負けたくはないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:53.22,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}終わらない夢が 胸のざわめきが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:57.54,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}身体を巡って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:03.48,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}痛みさえ 今 強さになるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:08.04,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}信じた道を行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.98,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}私を突き動かす熱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:21.58,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}描き続けてきた 世界へ導く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.42,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}逝去的昔日无法复返
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:15.04,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}从松开双手那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.94,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}不再有能失去之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:25.18,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}如此不断反復詢問
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:31.82,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}寂静的水面浮映着一轮圆月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:37.18,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}一切的黑暗都能照亮驱散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:42.36,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}耀眼的光芒 照耀未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:47.18,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}正因不愿服输
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:53.22,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}没有终点的梦境与胸中的喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:57.54,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}萦绕全身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:03.48,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}曾经的伤痛如今已化为坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:08.04,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}朝着自己相信的道路进发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.98,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}鼓励我地这份热情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:21.58,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}引导你前往描绘中的世界
